重要声明 / Important Notice:
本仓库为「大乐透数据分析流程」的开源演示，所有号码与统计均为历史数据归档，
不预示未来开奖结果，不构成任何购彩建议。彩票为独立随机事件，请理性投注。
This repository is an open-source demonstration of a lottery data-analysis workflow.
All numbers and statistics are historical archives; they do not predict future
draws and constitute no betting advice. Lotteries are independent random events—play responsibly.
